catalogEntryView.name: Satin platform sandals
catalogEntryView.longDescription: These sandals characterized by a simple, feminine design and large bow with logo evoke retro moods. The ankle strap and thick heel complete the style with refined elegance.

Upper with bow and metal lettering logo
Fabric logo label
Leather and rubber sole
135 mm satin-covered heel
40 mm satin-covered platform
